snippet.title: KAKU: Ancient Seal Receives a Major Remake - New Demo now available!
snippet.description:
·Try our free demo on steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1179580/KAKU_Ancient_Seal/

Dear adventurers,
We are thrilled to announce brand new demo for KAKU: Ancient Seal, an Open-World ARPG filled with puzzles, challenges and epic fights already available in Early Access on Steam, and coming out in Full Released version this Summer 2024. 

·Check our game on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1179580/KAKU_Ancient_Seal/
·Follow KAKU: Ancient Seal on twitter: https://twitter.com/KakuAncientSeal
·Join our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/ADBCyPE4ha
